Gabelli group lifts General Host stake . A group led by New York investment manager Mario Gabelli said Thursday it raised its stake in General Host Corp to the equivalent of 3 , 408 , 572 common shares or 13 . 88 percent of the total outstanding . In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission , the group said its latest transactions include the purchase of a net of 270 , 499 common shares between September 13 and 24 at prices ranging from $ 2 . 625 to $ 2 . 80 a share . The group said its stake includes 1 , 310 , 518 common shares it will receive on conversion of General Host debentures that it holds . 
